      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your feelings of emptiness and disconnectedness are valid, but they do not mean your life has lost all meaning or that you are a ghost. This depth of grief often signals a need for compassion rather than further self-criticism, and you deserve to be heard without judgment. Please reach out to a mental health professional or a crisis line immediately, as they can provide the specialized support you need to navigate these overwhelming thoughts and find a path forward.",
